{
  "stem": "11593.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They'd even occupied most parts of our house for some of the which what you'd call a mayor in the city, until they get established.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Immediately, the education was stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No more Tarbut and no nationalistic school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to accept the Russian curriculum, which was basically a lot of propaganda, but mostly was not a bad curriculum.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The demand was great for literature, math.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the subjects were taught quite well, and the teachers were quite good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the discipline-- very high discipline.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As youngsters, we accepted that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We [? started ?] in the school-- in the school, and our life went on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's more or less the same-- you know, attending school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had some more meetings, you know, because the school demanded meetings to create-- to-- to spread their propaganda.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They ran more dance in the-- in school-- you know, parties at the school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the sports activities were basically the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember somebody used to try to have the youngsters work in the fields-- you know, get them to help the farmers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Our vacations, we used to spend, basically, at my grandmother's because the city [POLISH] was surrounded by forest, and it's supposed to be a vacation town because of pure air.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All this changed in June 21-- in June 21, 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The German army occupied our area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Ukrainian soldiers, [? capitalists, ?] and joined the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Jews and the Poles were being murdered and hunted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Immediately, the Germans installed the [POLISH] commissar in-- in charge of the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They set up a new establishment, a new government, in the-- with the headquarters in Rovno, which was the headquarters for a certain region incorporating Rovno and Dubno and certain towns.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then the people were extremely nervous.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
